WEBVTT

00:00:00.160 --> 00:00:02.669
Hey, good morning family. I'm excited to

00:00:02.679 --> 00:00:05.269
be with y'all again today. I have a

00:00:05.279 --> 00:00:08.390
part two of the video that I did

00:00:08.400 --> 00:00:11.270
yesterday or two days ago, whenever I'm

00:00:11.280 --> 00:00:13.509
releasing this. I'm going to tell you the

00:00:13.519 --> 00:00:16.670
political stuff about what I saw

00:00:16.670 --> 00:00:16.680
for

00:00:16.680 --> 00:00:19.790
2024. Like I said, I'm a

00:00:19.800 --> 00:00:22.150
prophetic intercessor, and the Lord shows

00:00:22.160 --> 00:00:25.589
me things to pray about. I pray

00:00:25.599 --> 00:00:27.710
for the nation, the economy,

00:00:27.710 --> 00:00:27.720
and

00:00:27.720 --> 00:00:30.070
people's healings—everything

00:00:30.070 --> 00:00:30.080
that's

00:00:30.080 --> 00:00:31.950
on His

00:00:31.960 --> 00:00:34.190
heart for that day. He will show me

00:00:34.200 --> 00:00:36.389
things to come; He does it all the time.

00:00:36.399 --> 00:00:39.950
This is my life and this is what I do.

00:00:39.960 --> 00:00:42.790
I'm praying over 2024 right now, and I

00:00:42.790 --> 00:00:42.800
pray

00:00:42.800 --> 00:00:44.910
at this time

00:00:44.920 --> 00:00:47.470
every single year. This is my

00:00:47.480 --> 00:00:49.790
prayer topic; I start praying for the

00:00:49.800 --> 00:00:51.790
next year. These are the

00:00:51.800 --> 00:00:53.950
things that He's showed me so far. I'm sure

00:00:53.960 --> 00:00:56.549
I will get a lot more; it usually

00:00:56.549 --> 00:00:56.559
happens.

00:00:56.559 --> 00:00:59.709
This

00:00:59.719 --> 00:01:05.310
is what the Lord has showed me

00:01:05.320 --> 00:01:09.910
so far. I want to say this: I am not

00:01:09.920 --> 00:01:13.109
saying that this person will be the

00:01:13.119 --> 00:01:15.350
president of the United States because the

00:01:15.350 --> 00:01:15.360
Lord

00:01:15.360 --> 00:01:17.830
did not say that.

00:01:17.840 --> 00:01:20.350
I'm just telling you what I saw, and

00:01:20.360 --> 00:01:22.830
I'm not going to

00:01:22.840 --> 00:01:26.550
add to or take away from anything.

00:01:26.560 --> 00:01:30.870
I saw Michigan,

00:01:32.560 --> 00:01:37.069
Minnesota,

00:01:37.069 --> 00:01:37.079
and

00:01:37.079 --> 00:01:40.710
Ohio. All of a sudden, I saw

00:01:40.720 --> 00:01:47.109
people in red with white letters

00:01:47.119 --> 00:01:50.389
across their hats and shirts,

00:01:50.399 --> 00:01:53.149
but it was shiny.

00:01:53.159 --> 00:01:54.910
These shirts were shiny

00:01:54.920 --> 00:01:59.190
red, and it had

00:01:59.190 --> 00:01:59.200
MAGA

00:01:59.200 --> 00:02:03.990
written across it in big

00:02:04.000 --> 00:02:08.430
white letters. Between each letter

00:02:08.440 --> 00:02:11.029
was a star from the United States

00:02:11.039 --> 00:02:14.110
flag, that kind of star.

00:02:16.800 --> 00:02:19.589
I did not know

00:02:19.599 --> 00:02:22.110
what it was at first because I did not

00:02:22.120 --> 00:02:24.550
see the white letters until the Lord let

00:02:24.560 --> 00:02:26.589
me focus on it in the vision. When I

00:02:26.599 --> 00:02:29.910
was praying,

00:02:29.920 --> 00:02:32.190
I could see what the Lord was

00:02:32.200 --> 00:02:36.470
showing me was

00:02:36.470 --> 00:02:36.480
MAGA.

00:02:36.480 --> 00:02:40.430
It was on these shiny red things, and

00:02:40.440 --> 00:02:43.430
I could see it building.

00:02:45.920 --> 00:02:49.229
It was like waves; it was moving

00:02:49.239 --> 00:02:51.550
like when you're in a

00:02:51.560 --> 00:02:54.550
stadium and you see the Red Wave. It was like

00:02:54.560 --> 00:02:56.790
that,

00:02:59.120 --> 00:03:01.149
but it was

00:03:01.159 --> 00:03:04.149
growing over this area:

00:03:04.159 --> 00:03:06.630
Michigan, Detroit—all that up

00:03:06.640 --> 00:03:08.710
there. It was all starting to come together, and

00:03:08.720 --> 00:03:11.430
then all of a sudden, it started moving

00:03:11.440 --> 00:03:15.149
south

00:03:15.149 --> 00:03:15.159
to

00:03:15.159 --> 00:03:19.350
Iowa,

00:03:19.360 --> 00:03:22.670
Nebraska, and Kansas. Whenever

00:03:22.680 --> 00:03:24.110
it got to

00:03:24.120 --> 00:03:27.910
Oklahoma, I saw what looked like

00:03:27.920 --> 00:03:30.589
transparent

00:03:30.589 --> 00:03:30.599
embers.

00:03:30.599 --> 00:03:32.990
They were all over Oklahoma, but they

00:03:32.990 --> 00:03:33.000
looked

00:03:33.000 --> 00:03:35.789
like they were on fire, like

00:03:35.789 --> 00:03:35.799
embers

00:03:35.799 --> 00:03:41.070
that were on fire—embers like

00:03:41.070 --> 00:03:41.080
sap

00:03:41.080 --> 00:03:46.470
from maple trees. It

00:03:46.480 --> 00:03:48.309
looked like that, but you could see it

00:03:48.319 --> 00:03:51.990
was transparent over Oklahoma. These

00:03:52.000 --> 00:03:55.869
little red MAGA things turned into

00:03:55.879 --> 00:03:58.030
embers—help

00:03:58.040 --> 00:04:00.949
me, Holy

00:04:00.949 --> 00:04:00.959
Ghost—almost

00:04:00.959 --> 00:04:03.350
like candy. I don't know how

00:04:03.360 --> 00:04:05.910
else to say it, but it was all over,

00:04:05.910 --> 00:04:05.920
and

00:04:05.920 --> 00:04:09.670
then they caught fire. All

00:04:09.680 --> 00:04:13.149
those became like they were on fire, and

00:04:13.159 --> 00:04:15.910
I saw torches over this area. It

00:04:15.920 --> 00:04:18.390
was just over Oklahoma, which I thought

00:04:18.400 --> 00:04:20.789
was interesting. It went down into

00:04:20.799 --> 00:04:22.670
Texas a little bit, but it didn't cover

00:04:22.680 --> 00:04:24.710
it very much, just the North

00:04:24.710 --> 00:04:24.720
Dallas-Fort

00:04:24.720 --> 00:04:28.189
Worth area.

00:04:28.199 --> 00:04:30.270
I had a list of all the states

00:04:30.280 --> 00:04:35.270
that I saw turn red. I

00:04:35.270 --> 00:04:35.280
saw

00:04:35.280 --> 00:04:37.909
five states where I

00:04:37.909 --> 00:04:37.919
believe there was

00:04:37.919 --> 00:04:40.950
trouble.

00:04:40.950 --> 00:04:40.960
I

00:04:40.960 --> 00:04:43.629
saw

00:04:43.639 --> 00:04:47.870
Oregon, Washington, and California

00:04:47.880 --> 00:04:51.670
were instantaneously blue.

00:04:51.680 --> 00:04:55.469
Then I saw Hawaii blue, Alaska red, and

00:04:55.469 --> 00:04:55.479
I saw

00:04:55.479 --> 00:04:59.110
trouble in Arizona.

00:04:59.120 --> 00:05:02.070
This is what's interesting: Arizona

00:05:02.080 --> 00:05:05.629
turned blue, but there

00:05:05.639 --> 00:05:09.629
was red on top of the blue. It made

00:05:09.639 --> 00:05:13.870
it into a different shade of red,

00:05:13.880 --> 00:05:16.350
like the blue was turning red,

00:05:16.360 --> 00:05:18.270
a different

00:05:18.270 --> 00:05:18.280
crimson—a

00:05:18.280 --> 00:05:21.230
deeper red.

00:05:21.240 --> 00:05:24.990
I saw trouble there;

00:05:25.000 --> 00:05:27.510
that's all I can say about it. I saw New

00:05:27.520 --> 00:05:34.710
Mexico red, Utah red, Wyoming

00:05:34.720 --> 00:05:40.870
red, Colorado blue, Montana red,

00:05:40.870 --> 00:05:40.880
and

00:05:40.880 --> 00:05:43.749
Nevada

00:05:43.759 --> 00:05:49.590
turned blue. Idaho was red, then

00:05:49.590 --> 00:05:49.600
Texas

00:05:49.600 --> 00:05:52.110
went red, and then I

00:05:52.120 --> 00:05:56.309
saw it spread throughout the South.

00:05:56.319 --> 00:05:58.309
It was red, but I saw trouble in

00:05:58.319 --> 00:06:02.110
Georgia. It was like

00:06:02.120 --> 00:06:03.870
something was going on with Georgia

00:06:03.880 --> 00:06:06.230
again. Praying over Georgia, there

00:06:06.230 --> 00:06:06.240
were

00:06:06.240 --> 00:06:09.749
blue spots, but the main part of it was

00:06:09.759 --> 00:06:12.629
red, the way the people were

00:06:12.639 --> 00:06:15.830
voting, because I saw this

00:06:15.830 --> 00:06:15.840
MAGA.

00:06:15.840 --> 00:06:20.589
Then all of a sudden, I saw

00:06:20.599 --> 00:06:24.029
the storm over Donald Trump. Now, I'm

00:06:24.039 --> 00:06:27.350
going to tell you this: I did not see him

00:06:27.350 --> 00:06:27.360
as

00:06:27.360 --> 00:06:29.909
president. You can assume what you

00:06:29.909 --> 00:06:29.919
want

00:06:29.919 --> 00:06:32.029
because of the drama

00:06:32.039 --> 00:06:34.430
that happened in 2020, but I'm not getting

00:06:34.440 --> 00:06:36.589
into that. I'm just telling you what I

00:06:36.599 --> 00:06:40.029
saw so you can pray about

00:06:40.039 --> 00:06:41.469
it. If you believe that's what the

00:06:41.479 --> 00:06:44.230
Lord's saying, whatever, but I'm

00:06:44.240 --> 00:06:49.070
not saying he wins or loses.

00:06:49.080 --> 00:06:52.670
I heard the Spirit of the Lord

00:06:52.680 --> 00:06:57.070
say this: 'Can't

00:06:57.080 --> 00:07:00.430
you tell that this is a

00:07:00.430 --> 00:07:00.440
refiner's

00:07:00.440 --> 00:07:02.710
fire that he is going

00:07:02.720 --> 00:07:04.070
through right

00:07:04.080 --> 00:07:06.869
now? Don't you know that he is being

00:07:06.879 --> 00:07:10.390
molded in a refiner's

00:07:10.390 --> 00:07:10.400
fire?'I

00:07:10.400 --> 00:07:13.950
saw him through all

00:07:13.960 --> 00:07:15.670
the trials;

00:07:15.680 --> 00:07:17.869
I saw him going

00:07:17.879 --> 00:07:20.710
through the pressure on the potter's

00:07:20.710 --> 00:07:20.720
wheel,

00:07:20.720 --> 00:07:22.589
being

00:07:22.599 --> 00:07:27.350
molded, broken down, and humbled. All of a

00:07:27.360 --> 00:07:29.589
sudden, I saw the Lord Jesus and Donald

00:07:29.599 --> 00:07:32.710
Trump. I saw him on one knee,

00:07:32.720 --> 00:07:35.869
bent over with

00:07:37.759 --> 00:07:40.390
his head down,

00:07:40.400 --> 00:07:43.710
weeping before the Lord. I

00:07:43.720 --> 00:07:46.070
saw the Lord Jesus Christ touching

00:07:46.080 --> 00:07:49.710
Donald Trump's head as if He

00:07:51.599 --> 00:07:52.790
were

00:07:54.360 --> 00:07:58.430
anointing him. I saw

00:07:58.440 --> 00:08:00.149
a glow

00:08:00.159 --> 00:08:05.110
all around him while he was crying,

00:08:07.879 --> 00:08:10.029
kneeling before the Lord

00:08:15.159 --> 00:08:17.909
in a prayer stance like a Tim

00:08:17.909 --> 00:08:17.919
Tebow.

00:08:17.919 --> 00:08:20.270
I don't know

00:08:20.280 --> 00:08:23.110
how else to say it, but that's

00:08:23.120 --> 00:08:24.749
how he was before the Lord. He had

00:08:24.759 --> 00:08:27.790
a blue suit on with a white

00:08:27.800 --> 00:08:30.110
shirt and a red tie.

00:08:30.120 --> 00:08:32.870
He was

00:08:32.880 --> 00:08:34.870
praying, the Lord Jesus had

00:08:34.880 --> 00:08:37.870
His hand on his head, and I saw a glow all

00:08:37.880 --> 00:08:39.389
around

00:08:39.399 --> 00:08:42.269
him.

00:08:43.959 --> 00:08:49.030
I told you what I saw about

00:08:49.040 --> 00:08:52.590
Canada, America, and

00:08:52.600 --> 00:08:58.190
Mexico. I saw him trying to fix

00:08:58.200 --> 00:09:02.750
everything, getting

00:09:02.760 --> 00:09:06.430
downloads from the Lord like a

00:09:06.440 --> 00:09:09.550
Solomon. There was

00:09:09.560 --> 00:09:14.430
divine speaking to him on how to mend

00:09:14.440 --> 00:09:17.509
and fix everything that was destroyed.

00:09:17.519 --> 00:09:19.870
I

00:09:19.880 --> 00:09:24.230
saw tens of millions of people coming

00:09:24.240 --> 00:09:26.949
from the southern

00:09:26.959 --> 00:09:30.630
border trying to invade America over the

00:09:30.640 --> 00:09:36.269
next year. I'm talking

00:09:36.269 --> 00:09:36.279
about

00:09:36.279 --> 00:09:38.670
people from

00:09:38.680 --> 00:09:42.310
all over the world.

00:09:42.320 --> 00:09:46.269
I literally saw millions of people coming—so

00:09:46.269 --> 00:09:46.279
many

00:09:46.279 --> 00:09:49.389
that it

00:09:49.389 --> 00:09:49.399
was

00:09:49.399 --> 00:09:52.150
like

00:09:52.150 --> 00:09:52.160
a sea

00:09:52.160 --> 00:09:54.269
of

00:09:54.269 --> 00:09:54.279
people

00:09:54.279 --> 00:09:56.069
stacked upon

00:09:56.079 --> 00:09:59.750
each

00:09:59.760 --> 00:10:03.030
other,

00:10:03.040 --> 00:10:05.230
trying to come across

00:10:05.240 --> 00:10:07.750
the border all at once.

00:10:09.720 --> 00:10:11.190
There was nothing they could do.

00:10:12.560 --> 00:10:14.470
During this next year, 2024, this

00:10:14.480 --> 00:10:17.990
was what was happening.

00:10:18.000 --> 00:10:21.630
I could see

00:10:21.630 --> 00:10:21.640
that

00:10:21.640 --> 00:10:27.310
people like George Soros and Klaus

00:10:27.310 --> 00:10:27.320
Schwab and

00:10:27.320 --> 00:10:31.829
these other big people

00:10:31.839 --> 00:10:34.590
thought, 'It's done. There's

00:10:34.600 --> 00:10:36.790
nothing they can do to salvage

00:10:36.800 --> 00:10:39.069
America.

00:10:39.079 --> 00:10:41.389
We've accomplished what we

00:10:41.399 --> 00:10:45.150
needed to accomplish,'because the

00:10:45.160 --> 00:10:47.030
dollar was destroyed. Everything was

00:10:47.040 --> 00:10:49.310
destroyed; I saw fifty cents on the dollar.

00:10:49.320 --> 00:10:52.350
It was completely a

00:10:52.360 --> 00:10:56.470
depression. But out of what looked like

00:10:56.480 --> 00:11:00.750
complete devastation and no

00:11:00.750 --> 00:11:00.760
repair—like

00:11:00.760 --> 00:11:02.829
a

00:11:02.829 --> 00:11:02.839
TKO—I

00:11:02.839 --> 00:11:04.190
saw

00:11:04.200 --> 00:11:09.470
divine wisdom coming

00:11:09.470 --> 00:11:09.480
onto

00:11:09.480 --> 00:11:14.069
Donald Trump. I saw a glow around him, a

00:11:14.079 --> 00:11:17.150
Holy Ghost wisdom like

00:11:17.150 --> 00:11:17.160
Solomon's

00:11:17.160 --> 00:11:21.509
rising up in him on how to

00:11:21.519 --> 00:11:23.629
mend and fix

00:11:23.639 --> 00:11:27.190
things. Over

00:11:27.190 --> 00:11:27.200
that

00:11:27.200 --> 00:11:30.230
four-year

00:11:30.240 --> 00:11:32.310
period,

00:11:32.320 --> 00:11:38.110
2025 was awful, 2026 was not as bad,

00:11:38.110 --> 00:11:38.120
and

00:11:38.120 --> 00:11:42.509
2027 was getting better. By 2028, things

00:11:42.519 --> 00:11:45.230
were building back, though it was

00:11:45.240 --> 00:11:49.030
nothing compared to what it was.

00:11:49.040 --> 00:11:53.750
Thank you, Holy Spirit.

00:11:53.760 --> 00:11:57.110
He wouldn't

00:11:57.120 --> 00:12:00.190
let me see past that. I saw

00:12:00.200 --> 00:12:07.110
clouds and the glory in 2027 and 2028.

00:12:07.120 --> 00:12:12.750
It looked

00:12:12.760 --> 00:12:14.230
like clouds and

00:12:14.240 --> 00:12:16.670
thunderstorms growing

00:12:16.680 --> 00:12:18.350
in the spirit

00:12:18.350 --> 00:12:18.360
realm

00:12:18.360 --> 00:12:20.710
when I was praying,

00:12:20.720 --> 00:12:23.710
but He wouldn't let me look past it. Sometimes the

00:12:23.710 --> 00:12:23.720
Lord will

00:12:23.720 --> 00:12:26.150
let

00:12:26.160 --> 00:12:29.030
you,

00:12:29.040 --> 00:12:31.230
and sometimes He won't, but this

00:12:31.240 --> 00:12:33.110
time it was like, 'It's not time for

00:12:33.120 --> 00:12:35.470
you to see into that.'I was not

00:12:35.480 --> 00:12:37.870
allowed to look into it spiritually when

00:12:37.880 --> 00:12:42.389
praying. I saw

00:12:42.399 --> 00:12:45.230
April of

00:12:45.240 --> 00:12:49.949
2024; I saw the eclipse, and behind the

00:12:49.959 --> 00:12:52.509
eclipse, I saw the darkness

00:12:52.519 --> 00:12:56.990
going over America. I saw a

00:12:57.000 --> 00:13:01.230
storm in front of the eclipse,

00:13:01.240 --> 00:13:03.829
the most vicious

00:13:03.839 --> 00:13:06.350
storm that I've ever seen

00:13:06.350 --> 00:13:06.360
in

00:13:06.360 --> 00:13:08.670
the spirit realm.

00:13:08.680 --> 00:13:11.230
There was lightning shooting

00:13:11.230 --> 00:13:11.240
out—an

00:13:11.240 --> 00:13:13.509
electric storm. The

00:13:13.519 --> 00:13:16.189
lightning was so fierce and

00:13:16.199 --> 00:13:18.710
intense that some of the lightning bolts

00:13:18.720 --> 00:13:22.230
were frozen in time coming out of the

00:13:22.240 --> 00:13:25.230
cloud covering the

00:13:25.240 --> 00:13:27.949
eclipse. I don't know what this meant,

00:13:27.959 --> 00:13:31.829
but it was interesting.

00:13:31.839 --> 00:13:35.350
Behind the cloud, the eclipse was

00:13:35.360 --> 00:13:38.430
gold. I could see colors of gold,

00:13:38.440 --> 00:13:41.150
red, and yellow from

00:13:41.160 --> 00:13:44.910
the sun

00:13:44.910 --> 00:13:44.920
and

00:13:44.920 --> 00:13:48.790
moon. You

00:13:48.800 --> 00:13:51.949
could see the eclipse happening, but you

00:13:51.959 --> 00:13:53.670
couldn't really make it out because the

00:13:53.680 --> 00:13:57.509
storm was so intense in front of

00:13:57.519 --> 00:13:59.990
it.

00:14:00.000 --> 00:14:01.990
It was just lightning

00:14:03.600 --> 00:14:06.269
in front of this eclipse

00:14:06.279 --> 00:14:08.350
taking place over America in

00:14:08.360 --> 00:14:11.230
2024. You can add up

00:14:11.240 --> 00:14:14.949
what you want about it. I

00:14:14.959 --> 00:14:16.870
have not seen

00:14:16.880 --> 00:14:19.790
Gavin

00:14:19.790 --> 00:14:19.800
or

00:14:19.800 --> 00:14:21.870
Michelle

00:14:21.880 --> 00:14:25.269
anymore when I pray. Like

00:14:25.279 --> 00:14:27.829
I said, I'm a prophetic intercessor; I see

00:14:27.839 --> 00:14:29.629
these things and I know we can change

00:14:29.639 --> 00:14:31.749
some things,

00:14:31.749 --> 00:14:31.759
though

00:14:31.759 --> 00:14:34.269
some things we can't. I saw

00:14:34.279 --> 00:14:35.590
him

00:14:35.600 --> 00:14:38.470
forever up

00:14:38.480 --> 00:14:41.749
until a month ago, almost every

00:14:41.759 --> 00:14:43.150
time I prayed.

00:14:43.150 --> 00:14:43.160
After

